casebody.data:
STATE of Arizona
v.
Joshua Wayne REDZINAK CR-18-0299-PR Supreme Court of Arizona. October 30, 2018

FURTHER ORDERED: The Court of Appeals' Opinion shall not be published, pursuant *502to Rule 111(g), Arizona Rules of the Supreme Court.

FURTHER ORDERED remanding to the trial court to recalculate the term of probation in light of the State's confession of error. Justice Gould voted to grant review and not to depublish or remand.
